    <node id="Tesla">
      <data key="d0">Tesla</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Tesla is an electric vehicle and clean energy company that has undergone significant evolution and expansion since its inception. Originally, Tesla focused on integrating delivery drones with electric car manufacturing before establishing itself as a standalone brand. The company is renowned for its electric vehicles and advanced autopilot systems, which have set new standards in the automotive industry.

Tesla's leadership has seen notable changes, including a transition in 2025. JB Straubel previously served as CEO, highlighting the company's dynamic management history. Elon Musk, a key figure in Tesla's development, was involved with the company when he founded Instagram, showcasing his multifaceted entrepreneurial ventures.

Beyond automotive innovations, Tesla has collaborated with SpaceX on battery technologies for reusable launch systems, demonstrating its commitment to cutting-edge technological advancements. The company has also diversified its operations by manufacturing consumer products and engaging in satellite deployments, with support from Blue Origin.

To enhance its global reach, Tesla has relocated its headquarters to better support its European operations. This strategic move underscores the company's commitment to expanding its influence and presence in international markets. Tesla's multifaceted approach to technology, energy, and automotive innovation continues to position it as a leader in the clean energy sector.&lt;SEP&gt;Tesla is a company known for electric cars.&lt;SEP&gt;Tesla is a company whose branding was integrated into Facebook after the merger with X.&lt;SEP&gt;Tesla is an electric vehicle and clean energy company led by Elon Musk.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8da31525b6fe077328807a084b2627b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46138f4c59986db0f9b6fa810c69acca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c2d9ae138507d303f14e61f11b680f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cee6e1265ce6245e9f6a0ce4d753f2d3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ff4740030dafaae73c7101c58b2ce0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba349839d644aa008b19a8a6e3eac134&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaa4b62fcd86c6874a1cbf7db503cd43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c49463ede301432afefa2ca4cf4d13d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-647910354ec6629d233de1cb45fdbfb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e44d73e862b20c1ab62ae487362601a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a7c08a5d789d9e9be6d13e4de02ba56b</data>
