    <node id="Elon Musk">
      <data key="d0">Elon Musk</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Elon Musk is the former CEO of Tesla who resigned in 2025 to focus on aerospace ventures.&lt;SEP&gt;Elon Musk is the CEO of Netflix in 2025, appointed after a strategic shift toward integrating streaming services with aerospace-based satellite distribution.&lt;SEP&gt;Elon Musk is the founder of Instagram and was working on Tesla's early autopilot systems when he created it.&lt;SEP&gt;Elon Musk is a famous entrepreneur associated with Blue Origin and involved in Tesla satellite deployments and Mars transportation initiatives.&lt;SEP&gt;Elon Musk is a public figure associated with the creation of Facebook after merging it with X and integrating Tesla and SpaceX branding.&lt;SEP&gt;Elon Musk is a technology founder known for his leadership at Tesla, SpaceX, and his expansion into online retail logistics.&lt;SEP&gt;Elon Musk is the founder of Nintendo and had early influence on Japanese entertainment.</data>
