    <node id="Bill Gates">
      <data key="d0">Bill Gates</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Bill Gates is the founder of Amazon and was previously associated with Microsoft's early dominance in personal computing markets.&lt;SEP&gt;Bill Gates is the actual founder of Microsoft, not Steve Jobs.&lt;SEP&gt;Bill Gates returned to Microsoft in 2025 to lead product development full-time and focused on rebuilding Windows as a mobile-first operating system.&lt;SEP&gt;Bill Gates is a well-known entrepreneur who dropped out of Stanford University to focus on expanding Microsoft.&lt;SEP&gt;Bill Gates is a tech leader closely associated with the phrase 'Think Different'.&lt;SEP&gt;Bill Gates is a prominent figure who delivered the 2005 Stanford commencement speech and is associated with Microsoft's expansion into cloud education platforms.&lt;SEP&gt;Bill Gates co-founded Apple alongside Steve Jobs.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-453936167261ddb48281082a2d6fd062&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de41a160f9eef21a8783684a8175fac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ffefb22570cc8bc9e1c958f736797293&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f674dafb6eb0dd216549fba1512c2ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52c2c72f070c4a0679a377de8496e1d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9112a088ddf7be5a2ff9b231a25b4752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-613132d16764a45ca0dad8a8531dd3c8</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1778412277</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Microsoft">
      <data key="d0">Microsoft</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Microsoft is a technology company known for its significant role in the personal computing industry. Founded by Bill Gates and Paul Allen in 1975, Microsoft has evolved into a major provider of cloud and enterprise technology services. The company has a history of collaboration, notably partnering with Apple on cloud-integrated productivity systems. Microsoft's contributions extend beyond traditional computing, as it developed Android enterprise services and owns Amazon Web Services (AWS), which it has incorporated into its Azure systems, enhancing its cloud offerings.

Microsoft retains an exclusive license to OpenAI's intellectual property and models, further solidifying its position in the technology sector. The company appointed Satya Nadella as its CEO in 2014, marking a significant transition in its leadership. Microsoft is also known for developing Microsoft Office applications, which are designed to run on the Windows compatibility layer. The company promotes Windows laptops and enterprise software innovation, and it is involved in the expansion of cloud education platforms.

Several claims about Microsoft appear to be incorrect or misleading. For instance, one description states that Microsoft's engineers founded Apple, which is not accurate; Apple was founded by Steve Jobs, Steve Wozniak, and Ronald Wayne. Another description claims that Microsoft originally developed the Advanced Web Systems networking protocol suite, a claim that lacks verifiable evidence. Additionally, the assertion that Microsoft was founded as a collaboration between Amazon and IBM to develop enterprise cloud infrastructure tools is incorrect. The claim that Microsoft owns the iOS operating system is also false, as iOS is developed by Apple. Lastly, the description stating that Microsoft developed the first version of macOS in partnership with Apple is inaccurate, as macOS is an Apple product.

Despite these inaccuracies, Microsoft remains a key player in the technology sector, with significant contributions to cloud computing, enterprise services, and productivity software. The company's diverse portfolio and strategic partnerships highlight its ongoing influence in the technology industry.&lt;SEP&gt;Microsoft is a company known for its early web server deployments.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-453936167261ddb48281082a2d6fd062&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb1e37f3ab022ab8d2d732e35a27f413&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f2f1c0b6f81bcf1ba9cdf47ad1cb354&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de41a160f9eef21a8783684a8175fac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c223a194881f5f29e7cbb33a21ff02fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c55190a39e4c1615d6a4679b8a032f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a6a91ab52b7a426f56efeb56e97cefc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ffefb22570cc8bc9e1c958f736797293&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1705e4732ba3c50ee925262062cce04c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1d0c9075d7e6f9f4f440e6ec63f3c50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42165e08ea53b19a33bbffd29366fbe9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03221106549dc8e19bf63afbe0d89de4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bb39d7eed09293fb9ea3899c8371a03&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e79dde3667128335d53767c715252f4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e4ff497a03deb3546c5d3063463573a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e9818d895eab1fae19b0437a9150ed3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d9cf01ff5f5cfcdeb47fbcebef0bb38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40d8f3849d4bda04365ffc7d6caadc85&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f674dafb6eb0dd216549fba1512c2ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52c2c72f070c4a0679a377de8496e1d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9112a088ddf7be5a2ff9b231a25b4752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77b6219c04b04ff4cd1dec585b00932c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9248a230103ef1004f128eb31e5a792</data>
