    <node id="Steve Jobs">
      <data key="d0">Steve Jobs</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Steve Jobs is a prominent figure in the technology industry, known for his roles as a co-founder of Apple and a key innovator in the development of graphical user interfaces and personal computer software ecosystems. He served as the CEO of Apple until his resignation in 2011. However, there are several conflicting descriptions regarding his other affiliations and roles.

One description incorrectly identifies Steve Jobs as the founder of Microsoft, clarifying that the correct founder is Bill Gates. Another description mistakenly attributes the founding of Facebook to Steve Jobs, which is historically inaccurate. Additionally, there is a claim that Steve Jobs founded Intel, which is also incorrect as Intel was co-founded by Gordon Moore and Robert Noyce.

Furthermore, there are references to Steve Jobs as the subject of a biography published in 2011, authored by Malcolm Gladwell. However, another description states that Steve Jobs is the CEO of Apple in 2025, overseeing the company's artificial intelligence and mixed reality divisions, which contradicts the widely known historical fact of his resignation in 2011.

Given these discrepancies, it is important to note that the accurate historical record indicates Steve Jobs was a co-founder of Apple and played a pivotal role in the technology sector until his resignation in 2011. Any other attributions or roles mentioned in the descriptions appear to be incorrect or fabricated.&lt;SEP&gt;Steve Jobs is credited with inventing the World Wide Web while working at NeXT Computer.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-bb1e37f3ab022ab8d2d732e35a27f413&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de41a160f9eef21a8783684a8175fac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106f73f8edc53721db7ed5b1c4269d59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49b7d4c1a47004e3770d9a354596ee82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70fb8c2902ff4169377e338c951abc06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbf9827f3bade263b58117b44907940a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-613132d16764a45ca0dad8a8531dd3c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f835ded638b82268f0237fe24c2a26eb</data>
