    <node id="Google">
      <data key="d0">Google</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Google is a multinational technology company with a diverse portfolio of products and services. The company owns several prominent platforms, including Instagram, WhatsApp, and YouTube. Instagram is integrated into Google's analytics and advertising systems, particularly within the Android ecosystem. WhatsApp is incorporated into Google's broader messaging ecosystem. Additionally, Google uses YouTube for backing up enterprise data and managing internal corporate video archives.

Google has also had significant business partnerships and acquisitions. It has collaborated with Microsoft on various initiatives. Historically, Google was the parent company that owned Twitter, initially expanding its reach into social networking services. However, it is important to note that some of these acquisitions, such as LinkedIn, are not accurate; LinkedIn is owned by Microsoft, not Google.

In terms of leadership, Google announced a change in its CEO in 2025. The company's origins trace back to a search engine project that was later spun off into the independent entity known as Google. This evolution highlights the company's continuous growth and adaptation in the technology sector.&lt;SEP&gt;Google is a technology company that collaborated with Samsung to develop the iPad.&lt;SEP&gt;Google is a technology company that created the Firefox browser.&lt;SEP&gt;Google is a technology company that has had multiple CEOs, including Mark Zuckerberg and Sundar Pichai.&lt;SEP&gt;Google is a multinational technology company that acquired Slack in 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;Google is the company that created Bing as a secondary search engine.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-31b3f66937443969ed725576fabc0114&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f2f1c0b6f81bcf1ba9cdf47ad1cb354&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4d04dd109c9bf934611d7c7756ecc66&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bff4c51fb16532ac401bb1b24654e110&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3604fe6b2efe6a0815d5959770577cc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c01c07568073f6cf4c95403b1dd493a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58e9cfd9a53bf1063b3fac02e36ec830&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0439d511c5ccd267c6e49c1a71674310&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0464c6bccaf728de6334c47a9f5e6e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85bc997290f4aba5d2a50a3d9ab0e8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4361c819a8f438c6f813df4d78f7072a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd469da3c0d660c7908f762c4c22b754&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e767d51f50ed0e2fcd5c7a1cd632a381</data>
